&lt;p&gt;Due to a rapid expansion of our international nurse’s programme an exciting opportunity has arisen for a fixed short term NHSP position within the corporate education team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking 3 Band 6 Nurses who are highly motivated and excited by new challenges with a passion for education and practice development&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role will support the delivery of the PD&amp;E’s team’s education and will focus upon support in our very successful international nurses programme and international nurses  bridging programme  .&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ideally you will have experience in delivering  teaching programmes including the assessment of clinical skills.  In addition you will have recent clinical practice experience, are a strong team player and an interest in gaining experience at a corporate level.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you would like to discuss this exciting opportunity please contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Fiona Creed Academic Programme Lead Fiona.creed@ouh.nhs.uk tel: 01865 227817&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hayley Harvey International Nurse programme lead  Hayley.harvey2@ouh.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
